<section id="work-topnav" data-nv-page="true" data-nv-page-state="scrollable" data-nv-state="close"
         data-nv-dial-target="topNavClosePlaceholder" data-nv-nav-state="hidden" data-nv-dial-responsive="true"
         class="expand-container work-item">
    <div class="expand-contianer__content cf">
        <div id="topNavClosePlaceholder" class="work-closeTarget"></div>
        <section data-nv-bgimage="true" data-nv-parallaximg="true" class="work-heroImage work-heroImage--topnav">
            <h1 class="topnav-header header-main header-large">
                Top Navigation Redesign
            </h1>
            <h2 class="topnav-subHeader header-secondary">
                Enhance Grand & Toy's top navigation by adopting minimalistic styling
                so that it better aligns with Grand & Toy's brand vision.
            </h2>
            <div class="work-IndicatorContainer">
                <div class="scroll-indicator scroll-indicator--dark">
                    <span>Scroll</span>
                    <span class="scroll-indicator__line"></span>
                    <span class="scroll-indicator__circle"></span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="topnav__screensContainer cf">
            <div data-nv-bgimage="true" data-nv-animate="true" class="topnav__screens"></div>
            <div class="work-IndicatorContainer">
                <div class="scroll-indicator scroll-indicator--dark">
                    <span>Scroll</span>
                    <span class="scroll-indicator__line"></span>
                    <span class="scroll-indicator__circle"></span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <div class="topnav__finalScreensContainer cf">
            <h1 class="topnav-header header-main--onDark header-large">
                Enhanced Navigation
            </h1>
            <br /><br />
            <div class="topnav__videoContainer">
                <video width="100%" autoplay loop muted>
                    <source src="/Content/Videos/topnav-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                    Your browser does not support the video tag.
                </video>
            </div>
            <br /><br />
            <section class="topnav__summaryContainer-content">
                <h1 class="header-main--onDark header-large">Company</h1>
                <p class="text-primary--OnDark">
                    Grand &amp; Toy (
                    <a href="https://www.grandandtoy.com" alt="Grand & Toy Home Page" class="link--blue" target="_blank" data-nv-ignore="true">
                        www.grandandtoy.com
                    </a>
                    )
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="topnav__summaryContainer-content">
                <h1 class="header-main--onDark header-large">My Role In Project</h1>
                <p class="text-primary--OnDark">
                    Lead Front End UI Developer
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="topnav__summaryContainer-content">
                <h1 class="header-main--onDark header-large">Enhancement Highlights</h1>
                <ul class="hr__summaryText list-spacious list-unstyled text-primary--OnDark">
                    <li>
                        1) By using minimalistic styling and enlarging the search bar, we can move the focal 
                        point from the navigation bar to the search bar. This better aligns with the business 
                        requirement of guiding the user to search for products instead of going through each 
                        category.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        2) The hero banner now stands out more due to the use of minimalistic design.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        3) The new top navigation also includes third level categories right in the navigation 
                        bar. This makes it easier for the user to see what is in a category without having to 
                        land on the category page.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        4) The new top navigation organizes different sections of the website, unlike the 
                        previous iteration where most of the sections were contained in the navigation bar.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        5) Interaction design has also been introduced to help guide the users' eyes as they 
                        interact with the top navigation.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        6) Enhanced performance due to removing all the product images contained within the 
                        top navigation.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        7) e-Merchandising now has a dedicated spot to advertise promotions such as deal center, 
                        or flash sale.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@Scripts.RenderFormat("<script src=\"{0}\" async></script>", "~/Content/workTopNav")